parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Torque Converter and Powertrain Control Module Failure
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the torque converter and powertrain control module can cause vibrations, shudders, and unusual noises while driving, which can lead to loss of control and accidents.

multiple axle replacements and alignments do not resolve the issue.
